    "summary": "**Topics:** 2025 overseas mobile game revenue rankings, market growth strategies for legacy vs. new titles, product lifecycle management in saturated markets, comparative analysis of successful market entry/revival pathways.\n**Entities:** Supercell, 《皇室战争》(Clash Royale), 《奔奔王国》(Kingshot), 点点数据 (data provider), and 30 specific mobile games listed in the TOP 30 table (e.g., Last War: Survival, Royal Match, 无尽冬日, 宝可梦TCG Pocket, Roblox, 荒野乱斗, Free Fire, 原神, etc.).\n**Dates:** 2025 (reporting year for the revenue data and rankings).\n**Claims & Definitions:** \n- Legacy product revival depends on deep, risk-tolerant reconstruction of core progression, gameplay, and economic systems.\n- New product breakthrough relies on precise micro-innovation atop validated models, paired with saturated marketing campaigns.\n- 《奔奔王国》 is the only new release to rank in the 2025 TOP 30.\n- 《皇室战争》 exemplifies the successful legacy product revitalization pathway.\n- Market growth opportunities are bifurcated: old products require systemic overhaul, while new products require targeted innovation + marketing synergy.\n**Tables & Metrics:** \n- Table: \"2025年海外移动游戏收入TOP30\" (2025 Overseas Mobile Game Revenue TOP 30), structured in three columns covering ranks 1–30.\n- Metrics: Annual revenue (全年流水) in 亿元 (100M RMB). Key data points: #1 Last War: Survival (154.53), #2 Royal Match (116.11), #13 皇室战争 (46.40), #17 奔奔王国 (42.26), #30 文明霸业 (28.89).\n**Evidence Types:** Ranked revenue table, comparative market strategy analysis, proprietary research attribution (点点数据自主研究及绘制)."
